Technical Procedure & Commands:
Step 1: Interface Initialization
Started the packet analyzer in the background via terminal:
Wireshark 
Step 2: Database Setup
Initialized the framework database to manage session logs:
msfdb init
Step 3: Framework Access
Launched the Metasploit console from the command line:
msfconsole
Step 4: Module Configuration
Executed commands to select the exploit and configure target parameters:
use exploit/[module_path]
set RHOSTS [target_ip]
set LHOST [your_ip]
show options
Step 5: Final Execution
Triggered the exploit command and verified the active session status:
exploit
sessions -l

